## Frontend vs Backend Logic

| Frontend (LWC)     | Backend (Apex)      |
| ------------------ | ------------------- |
| HTML UI Components | Apex Classes        |
| CSS Styling        | Database Operations |
| JavaScript Logic   | Business Logic      |
| User Interaction   | Data Processing     |
| Form Validation    | Record Management   |
| Event Handling     | Integrations        |

### Frontend Example

```javascript
handleClick() {
    this.message = 'Button Clicked';
}
```

### Backend Example

```apex
public with sharing class AccountController {
    @AuraEnabled
    public static List<Account> getAccounts() {
        return [SELECT Id, Name FROM Account];
    }
}
```

### Interaction Flow

```text
User
 ↓
LWC Component
 ↓
JavaScript Controller
 ↓
Apex Class
 ↓
Salesforce Database
 ↓
Response to LWC
 ↓
Updated UI
```

